===Etymology 1===
<div style="float:right;">
{{wikipedia|lang=ja}}
{{wikipedia|Horse}}
[[File:Nokota Horses cropped.jpg|thumb|250px|{{lang|ja|馬}} (''uma'', ''muma''): a pair of '''[[horse]]s'''.]]
